dmca.title: NetEnforcers complains of Planet Audio images in Froogle
dmca.body:
From:	[private] [[private]@netenforcers.com]
Sent:	Wednesday, September 14, 2005 5:21 PM
To:	'[private]'
Subject: Image Copyright Infringement - (Planet Audio)
Attn: Legal, DMCA complaints

I, the undersigned, CERTIFY UNDER PENALTY OF PERJURY that I am an agent authorized to act on behalf of the owner of certain intellectual property rights, said owner being named [Planet Audio] ("IP Owner"). I have a good faith belief that the listings or materials listed below are not authorized by the above IP Owner, its agent, or the law and therefore infringe the IP Owner's rights according to state,
federal, or United States law. Please act expeditiously to remove or disable access to the material or items claimed to be infringing.
Identity of advertisement(s) at issue/Images owned by [Planet Audio]/:

Electronic Express http://froogle.google.com/froogle_image?q=http://www.electronicexpress.com/images/products/large/6091.jpg&dhm=55a96fb9
http://froogle.google.com/froogle_image?q=http://www.electronicexpress.com/images/products/large/5853.jpg&dhm=eace3ff9
